 (1,3,2,1,'2011-12-02','<p class=\"\\\"><span><strong><span>Project:<span>Â Â Â Â Â Â  </span>Social Media</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<h3><span><span><span>Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â  </span></span></span><span>Activities this period</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span>Incorporated additional comments from the Stakeholder Engagement team into the New Media Strategy on 11/29/11. Incorporated Public Affairs comments and provided notes to Alâ€™Tariq regarding comments on 11/29/11.<span>Â  </span>Provide Alâ€™Tariq with updated New Media Strategy for review on 11/29/11.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span>Â </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><strong>Â </strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><strong>Project:<span>Â Â Â Â Â Â  </span>SLM</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><strong><span><span>Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â  </span>Activities this period</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span>Met with Fred & Sayed to discuss SLM feedback on 11/28/11.<span>Â  </span>Sayed stated that Diane and Taqueer would also be reviewing it and providing feedback.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span>Â </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><span>Â </span>Met with Fred & Alâ€™Tariq to discuss SLM and CPIC alignment on 11/28/11.<span>Â  </span>Sent information for clarification to Alâ€™Tariq. â€œ</span><span><span>Per CPIC, the ITIB reviews a project to approve a Mission Needs Statement and when the Exhibit 300 information is complete.Â  Exhibit 300/ITIB presentation requirements along with specific artifact requirements are only met after the planning of the project is complete.Â  The process to get from the Mission Needs Statement to the Exhibit 300 is defined by the SLM.Â  The SLM process provides completed deliverables to CPIC after the Planning and Requirements Phases are complete. Â Essentially 570 guides the process through these phases and then coordinates with 550/CPIC to provide their requested deliverables only after those phases are complete.â€ </span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span>Â </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span>Met with Alâ€™Tariq, Fred and Mr. Lewis on 11/30/11 to discuss SLM and guidance of projects.<span>Â  </span>We all came to an agreement of what the process should incorporate and when the ITIB should be involved (Completion of Mission Needs Statement, Completion of Pre-Planning and Completion of Planning and Requirements).<span>Â  </span>We were instructed by Alâ€™Tariq to complete the IM and to notify the business that we are the point of contact for 500.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span>Â </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><strong>Project:<span>Â Â Â Â Â Â  </span>Geospatial Publication Investment (aka Geospatial Communication Tool)</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><strong><span><span>Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â  </span>Activities this period</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span>Left message with Beth on 11/28/11 in regards to status and scope definition. Discussed status with Alâ€™Tariq.<span>Â  </span>Discussed scope and responsibility of ITIB interpretation on 11/29/11 with Fred and Alâ€™Tariq to ensure we were providing proper guidance.<span>Â  </span>Alâ€™Tariq stated that we do not interpret ITIB decisions and any business should ask their AD.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span>Discussed GPI in the previously noted SLM meeting.<span>Â  </span>I provided Beth feedback to her request for status on 11/30/11.<span>Â  </span>I also provided guidance for communications as directed by Ronnie.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span>Per the direction of Mr. Samuels, I proceeded with development of SLM artifacts for the business.<span>Â  </span>I transferred information into the Project Management Plan and completed the information available to date on 12/1/11.<span>Â  </span>I created a Change Management Plan and Communications Plan on 12/1/11.<span>Â  </span>I created an Acquisitions Plan and Quality Management Plan on 12/2/11.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><span>Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â </span></span></span></p>','<p class=\"\\\"><span><strong><em><span>Project:<span>Â Â Â Â Â Â  </span>Social Media</span></em></strong></span></p>\r\n<h3><span><span>Â </span></span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><span><span>Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â  </span></span></span><strong><span>Accomplishments</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\">Provided Al\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\'Tariq with updated New Media Strategy for review 11/29/11.Â  He distributed it to teams.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span>Meetings and Presentations</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><strong><em>Project:<span>Â Â Â Â Â Â  </span>SLM</em></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><span><span>Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â  </span></span></span><strong><span>Accomplishments</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span>Worked with Fred to align artifacts to move forward with Geospatial Publication Investment<strong>.</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><strong><em>Project:<span>Â Â Â Â Â Â  </span>Geospatial Publication Investment (aka Geospatial Communication Tool)</em></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><strong><em><span><span>Â Â Â Â Â Â </span></span></em></strong></span><span><span><strong>Accomplishments</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<h3><span>Transferred information into the Project Management Plan and completed the information available to date on 12/1/11.<span>Â  C</span>reated a Change Management Plan and Communications Plan on 12/1/11.<span>Â  C</span>reated an Acquisitions Plan and Quality Management Plan on 12/2/11.</span></h3>','<p class=\"\\\"><span><strong><em><span>Project:<span>Â Â Â Â Â Â  </span>Social Media</span></em></strong></span></p>\r\n