 (19,6,1,1,'2012-01-27','<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; background-color: white; line-height: 14.4pt; text-indent: -0.25in;\">Brief meeting with Mr. Samuels and Naomi regarding CPIC comments on the SLM</span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"background-color: white; line-height: 14.4pt; text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt;\">Worked on providing a response to CPIC comments on the SLM. &nbsp;Will have Mr. Samuels review the draft response before we submit them to CPIC.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"background-color: white; line-height: 14.4pt; text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt;\">Had a Walk the walk meeting with our System Support.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"background-color: white; line-height: 14.4pt; text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt;\">Had a brief meeting with Naomi to review CPIC comments to the SLM.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"background-color: white; line-height: 14.4pt; text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt;\">Conversation via email with Gail from the NOC regarding their comments on the SLM. &nbsp;They will submit their comments in the near future.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"background-color: white; line-height: 14.4pt; text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt;\">Got help from Ken and Mike to find the location of where all IM\'s are located.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"background-color: white; line-height: 14.4pt; text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt;\">Completed a brief presention of the definitions that we have to present to Ms. Levine.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"background-color: white; line-height: 14.4pt; text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt;\">Fixing some error/corrections with the SLM submitted by our Data Administrator.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 14.4pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; background: whit