 (20,6,1,1,'2012-02-03','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Worked on providing a response to CPIC comments on the SLM. &nbsp;Will have Mr. Samuels review the draft response before we submit them to CPIC.</li>\r\n<li>Made some minor corrections to the SLM technical manual.</li>\r\n<li>Working on the SLM presenation for Ms. Levine that will contain the next few phases for her to review. &nbsp;We will be presenting this to her soon.</li>\r\n<li>Helped Mike review some software tools for a project he is working on.</li>\r\n<li>Worked on making some additional changes to the SLM handbook based on reviews from other reviewers.</li>\r\n<li>Worked on making a list of suggestions for our Walk the Walk Support group.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Completed a draft response to CPIC comments on the SLM and submitted draft to Mr. Samuels.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Had a meeting with Naomi to provide some wording to some of CPIC comments to the SLM as it relates to the PMBOC. 2-2-12</li>\r\n<li>Had a meeting with Mike to help him review some software tools for a project he is working on. 2-2-12</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>None at this time.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>None at this time.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',2,4,'2012-02-03 18:29:25',6,'2012-02-11 00:35:48'),
 (21,3,2,1,'2012-02-03','<p><strong>New Media</strong></p>\r\n<p>Finalized meeting with Neil, Ronnie and Janet along with a meeting with Ronnie and Carole Pfisterer Carter on 1/30/12.&nbsp; The meetings are scheduled for 2/16/12.</p>\r\n<p>Met with Al\'Tariq on 1/31/12 to discuss his meeting with Kaveh regarding his stance on the New Media Strategy.&nbsp; Kaveh conveyed that he and WO 600 would not support a New Media Strategy where internal and external efforts were combined.&nbsp; He stated that they had to be two separate strategies and that the external strategy would come from WO 600. I expressed concern that Ronnie is unaware of this as we move forward with the additional meetings.&nbsp; Al\'Tariq stated that he agreed that Ronnie needed to be made aware and that he would share the information with her.&nbsp; He also asked that I review the Strategy again and ensure that WO 600\'s objectives are incorporated.&nbsp; I reviewed the Strategy, ensured incorporation of all objectives and added WO-600\'s \'Strategies\' under Next Steps.&nbsp; This was submitted to Al\'Tariq for review on 2/1/12 for review.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tablets/Smartphones</strong></p>\r\n<p>Met with Brian and Al\'Tariq to discuss items needed for the Tablet and Smartphone Inventory on 1/31/12.&nbsp; Created a spreadsheet for tracking of Tablets and Iphones including a section for business need.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Geospatial Publication Investment</strong></p>\r\n<p>Discussed the need for a clear written scope with Beth on 2/1/12.&nbsp; Provided her with a request for a meeting on 2/3/12.&nbsp; We will be meeting on Tuesday 2/7/12.&nbsp; Provided her with notification that the ITIB will meet on 3/1/12.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Quicktime IM</strong></p>\r\n<p>Prepared an IM for the release of an application for remote access to Quicktime per Al\'Tariq\'s request on 2/2/12.&nbsp; Submitted it to Al\'Tariq on 2/2/12 and followed up with a meeting to discuss the language.&nbsp; He approved the IM but we did not have access to the needed attachments for the IM.&nbsp; Coordinated with DOI to get the needed attachments for the IM.&nbsp; Worked with Lauren on 2/3/12 to package the IM. This included preparation of a Note to Reviewer.&nbsp; Prepared an email on 2/3/12 announcing the release of the application and submitted it to Al\'Tariq for review.</p>\r\n<p><strong>SLM</strong></p>\r\n<p>Met with Fred on 2/1/12 and 2/2/12 to discuss CPIC\'s comments regarding the SLM.&nbsp; Reviewed responses and provided responses to Fred that were specific to Project Management Insitute\'s (PMI\'s) Project Management Body of Knowledge (PMBOK)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','<p><strong>New Media</strong></p>\r\n<p>Finalized meeting with Neil, Ronnie  and Janet along with a meeting with Ronnie and Carole Pfisterer Carter  on 1/30/12.&nbsp; The meetings are scheduled for 2/16/12.</p>\r\n<p>Met with  Al\'Tariq on 1/31/12 to discuss his meeting with Kaveh regarding his  stance on the New Media Strategy. He asked that I review the Strategy again and ensure that WO  600\'s objectives are incorporated.&nbsp; Reviewed the Strategy, ensured  incorporation of all objectives and added WO-600\'s \'Strategies\' under  Next Steps.&nbsp; This was submitted to Al\'Tariq for review on 2/1/12 for  review.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tablets/Smartphones</strong></p>\r\n<p>Created a spreadsheet for tracking of Tablets  and Iphones including a section for business need.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Geospatial Publication Investment</strong></p>\r\n<p>Discussed  the need for a clear written scope with Beth on 2/1/12.&nbsp; Provided her  with a request for a meeting on 2/3/12.&nbsp; We will be meeting on Tuesday  2/7/12.&nbsp; Provided her with notification that the ITIB will meet on  3/1/12.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Quicktime IM</strong></p>\r\n<p>Prepared an IM for the  release of an application for remote access to Quicktime per Al\'Tariq\'s  request on 2/2/12.&nbsp; Submitted it to Al\'Tariq on 2/2/12 and followed up  with a meet